item.title: Compiler error
item.dc:creator: @pizza_pie pizza pie
item.description:
@pizza_pie wrote:

client.java:8994: cannot find symbol
symbol  : variable attackingPlayerId

Means exactly that. You have not declared a variable called [tt]attackingPlayerId[/tt]. Same for the other errors. Above that line, try declaring this:

int attackingPlayerId;

That might help

Same for the others.

It gives you that error because there is no variable by that name.
